Some tools needed to be installed before: 
    python3, 
    flask, 
    sqlite3

Getting start:
    type following commands in the commond window: 
        tar -xzvf todo_list.tar.gz
        cd todo_list

Using a new database:
    type following commands in the commond window: 
        rm db.sqlite3
        sqlite3 db.sqlite3 < schema.sql
        python3 rest_api.py
Using the same database:
    type following command in the commond window: 
        python3 rest_api.py
        
then open the url "http://localhost:8000" and use the website!